Sentencas: A one-equation model is proposed for fuel ejector in anode gas recirculation solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) system.
Titulo: Control oriented modeling of ejector in anode gas recirculation solid oxygen fuel cell systems

Sentencas: Firstly, the fundamental governing equations are established by employing the thermodynamic, fluid dynamic principles and chemical constraints inside the ejector; secondly, the one-equation model is derived by using the parameter analysis and lumped-parameter method.
Titulo: Control oriented modeling of ejector in anode gas recirculation solid oxygen fuel cell systems

Sentencas: Finally, the computational fluid dynamics (CFD) technique is employed to obtain the source data for determining the model parameters.
Titulo: Control oriented modeling of ejector in anode gas recirculation solid oxygen fuel cell systems

Sentencas: The effectiveness of the model is studied under a wide range of operation conditions.
Titulo: Control oriented modeling of ejector in anode gas recirculation solid oxygen fuel cell systems

Sentencas: The effect of ejector performance on the anode gas recirculation SOFC system is also discussed.
Titulo: Control oriented modeling of ejector in anode gas recirculation solid oxygen fuel cell systems

Sentencas: The presented model, which only contains four constant parameters, is useful in real-time control and optimization of fuel ejector in the anode gas recirculation SOFC system.
Titulo: Control oriented modeling of ejector in anode gas recirculation solid oxygen fuel cell systems
